--- updatePage called at 2026-03-24T05:44:56.276Z ---
INPUT: {
  "pageId": "b5188c59-aaa9-4008-a453-2d38b44bb4db",
  "blockType": "text",
  "data": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 1,
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "What is Machine Learning (ML)?"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Machine Learning (ML) is a subset of artificial intelligence (AI) that focuses on building systems that can learn from data. Instead of being explicitly programmed with rules, ML models learn patterns and relationships within data to make predictions or decisions."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2,
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "How Does it Work?"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "At its core, ML involves feeding large amounts of data to algorithms. These algorithms then analyze the data, identify patterns, and build a "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "model",
          "styles": {
            "italic": true,
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". This model can then be used to perform tasks like classification, regression, clustering, or anomaly detection on new, unseen data."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2,
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Key Types of Machine Learning"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 3,
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "1. Supervised Learning"
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Models are trained on labeled data, meaning each input example has a corresponding correct output."
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Used for tasks like predicting house prices (regression) or classifying emails as spam/not spam (classification)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 3,
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "2. Unsupervised Learning"
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Models are trained on unlabeled data and aim to find hidden patterns or structures within the data."
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Examples include customer segmentation (clustering) or dimensionality reduction."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 3,
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "3. Reinforcement Learning"
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "An agent learns to make decisions by performing actions in an environment and receiving rewards or penalties."
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Commonly used in robotics, game playing (e.g., AlphaGo), and autonomous driving."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2,
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Applications of ML"
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Recommendation systems (Netflix, Amazon)"
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Image and speech recognition (facial recognition, virtual assistants)"
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Medical diagnosis and drug discovery"
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Fraud detection"
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletListItem",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "Natural Language Processing (NLP)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": "ML continues to evolve rapidly, transforming industries and impacting daily life."
    }
  ]
}
